node.text: It’s PARTY TIME!! You did it again @mrrpmurphy I recommend giving @PromNetlfix a watch, which is out on Netlfix as your reading this. Can guarantee a fun colorful, jazzy time. Post your photo or video with #Zazzsquad to be featured! Let’s party this year out at home! #theProm#ad

A year ago today... I left to shoot a show called, Outer Banks. This is what happened.
. . .
 I really can’t put into words how I feel and how much love I have for everyone who was apart of this project. On and off camera. It’s a time to recognize and celebrate the hard work and heart that was put into this series. To everyone who watches it... THANK YOU! AND I HOPE YOU ENJOY IT!! @obx . . . 
Song: Suit and Jacket by Judah & the Lion

node.text:
Hello to all, 

I want to thank my amazing fans/followers who have shown nothing but love and support and are here for just a fun time. Unfortunately I’m here to call out the disrespect and harassment someone who I love dearly is getting on a daily basis. It has gotten to the degree where lies are being spread and accusations are being said that go beyond the normal “hate.” Not only is she not what she is being accused of being, she is the complete opposite and actively is so. Accusing someone you don’t know of being abusive and manipulative is not ok, especially when you don’t know the relationship personally. I’m very happy in the relationship I’m in. I know I might not actively show it on social platforms just how happy we are together, but this is my personal decision to keep most of those moments for myself. To those who are creating such displeasure and opinions about the one I love and my relationship, it’s time to stop. In this era of social engagement and enlightenment I want to express the importance to spread positivity and needing to know when it is unfair to express your own distaste for something or someone, especially when you can do it behind an anonymous identity. I was always told the best version of yourself is your most humbled self… I make this statement as my most humbled self and would be so grateful if we all would move forward in positivity and respect.

All love,
R

node.text:
TOMORROW BABY!!! 

two words -POGUE!MODE!- 
(And a shit ton more words)

This season has been brought to your screens by so many hard working mofos. And I’m so damn proud to be apart of this show because of them! Not only did we finish this season on time but we brought you ONE BANGER OF A SEASON!! So to ALL CAST AND CREW, I (pogue solute) YOU! Without further ado (in about 18 hours) 

OBX SEASON 2, HOPE YOU ENJOY!

Mucho thank you @flauntmagazine for letting me sport the sun hat… it’s what I felt was missing.

———(lil more of a serious note)———

Everyone Mother Earth needs a hand and we can help by being aware of how much we consume and throw away. What we can do to prevent more pollution from getting out there in our everyday lives is choose more eco friendly ways to consume and @newlight_technologies is working creating just that. #AirCarbon straws and utensils are now available for purchase. 

THANK YOU TO,
